item.title: Aglaosoma variegata
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: Large, hairy caterpillar found feeding on Cattle Bush (Alectryon oleifolius subsp. canescens). Size similar to adult pointer finger, both in length and girth. Thanks to Cathy Powers and Peter Marriott for identification.
